<Layout title="Membership">
  <h4>Benefits</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Receive one rotating member-exclusive sticker each year. Check out the one
      for 2024 here! You can receive yours in-person at any of our volunteer
      events. Please contact the volunteer coordinator when you arrive.
    </li>
    <li>Access to our organization's IT software.</li>
    <li>A personalized @friendsoflumspond.org email address and inbox.</li>
    <li>
      Ability to purchase member-exclusive merch such as volunteer shirts and
      stickers.
    </li>
    <li>
      Receive member-only communications such as voting, event planning, and
      organization changes.
    </li>
    <li>
      Be a part of a community that invests in nature and shares your love of
      the park.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Becoming a member</h3>

  <ul>
    <li>Apply using this form (TODO)</li>
    <li>
      Pay membership dues ($10 per year). Annual dues are due each year by April
      1st.
      <ul>
        <li>
          We recommend setting up your recurring dues online using our Donorbox
          form here. We also can accept cash and checks if desired.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
      purchase a volunteer shirt following the instructions below under "Member
      merchandise".
    </li>
    <li>
      Expect to receive an email within the next few days with our
      organization's onboarding documentation.
    </li>
    <li>
      If you have any questions or concerns, please send an email to <a
        href="mailto:membership@friendsoflumspond.org"
        >membership@friendsoflumspond.org</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>Thank you for being a friend of Lums Pond!</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Member merchandise</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>
      You can pick up your merchandise in-person at any of our volunteer events.
      Please contact the volunteer coordinator when you arrive.
    </li>
    <li>
      Merch can be purchased by members at any time. There is a chance you may
      need to wait for pickup if we need to order more.
    </li>
    <li>We can accept cash and checks for merch if desired.</li>
  </ul>

  <ol>
    <li>T-shirt (members only) / $15 for one, $50 for four</li>
    <li>Rotating member-exclusive sticker / $4 each</li>
    <li>Organization logo sticker / $4 each</li>
  </ol>
</Layout>
